%tr#comments
  %td{:colspan => "3"}
    %h6 Comments
    = form_tag comments_path, remote: true, class: 'comment-form' do
      = hidden_field_tag 'note_id', note.id
      .input-group.mb-3
        %input.form-control{:name => "comment", "aria-describedby" => "basic-addon3", "aria-label" => "Comment Text", :placeholder => "Comment Text", :type => "text"}/
        .input-group-append
          %button.btn.btn-outline-primary.comment-button{:href => "#", :role => "button", :type => "submit"} Add Comment
          //%a.btn.btn-danger{:href => "#", :role => "button"} Ã—

- note.comments.each do |comment|
  = render comment
